text: TKK can stand for: *Thrill Kill Kult, a common abbreviation for the electronic industrial band My Life With the Thrill Kill Kult *Teknillinen korkeakoulu (Helsinki University of Technology) - a former Finnish university *IATA Airport Code for Chuuk International Airport *Tanda Kecakapan Khusus, merit badge for Gerakan Pramuka Indonesian Scout Movement *Tokyu Corporation (Tokyo KyuKo Railway) *The Karate Kid, 1984 film *Thai Khem Khaeng, Thai economic investment program
title: TKK (disambiguation)
